{"tid":1814026,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★【樓舖齊冧】私樓平過居屋　外籍業主撤資　舖租瀉逾六成","createTime":"2020-01-06T16:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T04:48:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f531bf9aaeffb8b2b9394fb74aeba5ed1cce5e3","tid":1814026,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"踏入2020年，雖然樓市仍有創新高成交個案，但減價盤畢竟佔多數，有屯門私樓呎價更低過未補價居屋。舖市亦因零售寒冬而須大幅劈租，或許過了農曆新年後，相關個案會大幅增加。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【屯門海景花園呎售不足8千元】</span><br />\n屯門私樓呎價跌破8,000元，平過未補價居屋。祥益邱家邦稱，單位為海景花園4座低層A室，實用面積582方呎，日前獲區外首置客洽購，原業主擴闊議價空間，累積減價65萬元，單位終以465萬元成交，呎價7,990元。呎價料為2018年初後低位。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，同區居屋龍門居一個低層三房單位，實用面積592方呎，日前於未補價第二市場售480萬元，呎價8,108元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【港圖灣業主低14%沽貨離港】</span><br />\n社會亂局未止，有外籍業主撤資離港。土瓜灣港圖灣一個全海景單位，業主劈價170萬元，僅以980萬元沽出，低市價約14%，以實用面積602方呎計，呎價16,279元。"},{"pid":"3d69944e008f263a1683cbb1c4e6d829f4aac9c0","tid":1814026,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【東環又錄明賺實輸】</span><br />\n<br />\n東涌東環則再錄蝕使費個案，該行陳贊強表示，屋苑2A座連平台三房戶，實用面積535方呎，以755萬元易手，買家為外區換樓人士，呎價14,112元，單位4年僅升值約2%。<br />\n<br />\n此外，豪宅同樣要減價才獲承接，中原吳啟業表示，大埔康樂園18街雙號屋，實用面積1,389方呎，開價2,480萬元，累減230萬元，以2,250萬元沽，呎價16,199元。原業主於2013年以2千萬元入市，7年漲幅約12.5%。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【銅鑼灣舖租高位累挫八成】</span><br />\n<br />\n零售業市況持續惡化，主要購物區街舖租金大跌。銅鑼灣波斯富街一個交吉半年地舖，僅以每月約16萬元租出，較舊租大幅回落近六成半，成交呎租低至約160元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200106/bkn-20200106214151455-0106_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200106%2Fbkn-20200106214151455-0106_00842_001.html&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nOIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=7e160cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200106/bkn-20200106214151455-0106_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4164087542a4971a8b37215eb7d64cc583f6a30e","tid":1814026,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1288c223bc87885fac12a7feb3660789fdafde13","tid":1814026,"uid":35814,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"咁都叫冧？<br />\n之前炒高左<br />\n而家慢慢行番去正常價位啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda80e7a92244474afe00656c5376066d5f6e0da","tid":1814026,"uid":105121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:51:00.000Z","msg":"港圖灣好唔好住"},{"pid":"1c0a86f017af826af3dcf06e2c54023148cb16a0","tid":1814026,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:28:24.000Z","msg":"快了"},{"pid":"046fa379b33d442a2f90d9a25fc8193acefb241a","tid":1814026,"uid":42304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:31:40.000Z","msg":"仲好高，唔係後生仔世界"},{"pid":"ba61fb84f09d9fb52b59c8156d25c3c75013c47a","tid":1814026,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:34:45.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a6d4ab3c663c34826ded389a9bb70ef4b406c1","tid":1814026,"uid":213894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:47:13.000Z","msg":"仲入過黃金海岸同大欖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無車究竟點住呢啲地方"},{"pid":"9275bee1579c8fbad5c913215b3e7d57f06fc750","tid":1814026,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:50:08.000Z","msg":"分分